WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
CRS Explorer - A new tool to discover clinical research sites (CRSs) around the world.

00:00:03.033 --> 00:00:06.000
Click the About icon to find more information about CRS Explorer application.

00:00:09.160 --> 00:00:13.241
Click the Glossary icon to find in-depth information about terms and acronyms.

00:00:13.676 --> 00:00:15.440
Click the Explore icon to launch the CRS Explorer application.

00:00:15.680 --> 00:00:22.560
Click on the left navigation to search for specific CRSs.

00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:29.415
Click on any of the Pins on the map to find detailed information about an individual CRS.

00:00:29.445 --> 00:00:35.634
Click the Pharmacy icon to view pharmacy details.

00:00:35.901 --> 00:00:38.947
Click the Globe icon to return to the Explore view of the application.

00:00:38.947 --> 00:00:48.854
Filter and search for CRSs by Network, Region, and Risk Factors.

00:01:07.830 --> 00:01:13.915
Click on the Search icon to see the results in a list view.

00:01:13.975 --> 00:01:18.943
Click on the Favorite icon to add a CRS to a list of your favorite sites.

00:01:18.943 --> 00:01:23.818
Click on the Excel icon to export the site information to a report.

00:01:28.647 --> 00:01:38.793
Click the Chart icon to view data visualization, changing filters will update the chart.      

00:01:38.944 --> 00:01:43.444
